Each kali of our Light Pink and Mint Green Gharara Suit has been rendered in dull gold foliage shaped motifs that fall into a thich geometric border wrought using hexagon shaped gotta bootis, finished with a ring shaped lace. The gharara has been replenished with an embroidered chatta patti border. This sublime green dupatta featuring a jaal of round embellishments and a laced border in shades of silver and pink, adds a certain edge to the  ensemble.
Shop now exclusively at Lashkaraa.com

Our Hot Pink Embroidered Short Lehenga is the perfect ensemble for your mehendi event. The cropped choli has been subtly emblazoned with traditional marodi bootis and a beads finish on the hem. The lehenga features  an amalgam of different embroidery styles in floral and geometric patterns with elements of sequins and zari. The light pink dupatta serves as undertone to keep the look sassy and stylish.
Shop now exclusively at Lashkaraa.com
